OL,3,C#5 billion welfare cuts needed to
OL,4,C'save' system, Kendall to say
OL,6,FThe Work and Pensions Secretary will
OL,7,Fstand firm on Labour's #5 billion
OL,8,Fplans for welfare cuts on Wednesday,
OL,9,Farguing that reform is needed to make
OL,10,Fsure the system survives.
OL,12,FLiz Kendall is expected to say there
OL,13,Fis a "risk" the welfare state would
OL,14,Fcollapse without the proposed changes,
OL,15,Fwhich include tightening the
OL,16,Feligibility criteria for the main
OL,17,Fdisability benefit in England, the
OL,18,Fpersonal independence payment (Pip).
