OL,3,C#5 billion welfare cuts needed to
OL,4,C'save' system, Kendall to say
OL,6,FRestricting Pip would slash benefits
OL,7,Ffor about 800,000 people, while the
OL,8,Fsickness-related element of universal
OL,9,Fcredit is also set to be cut.
OL,11,FThe package of measures is aimed at
OL,12,Freducing the number of working-age
OL,13,Fpeople on sickness benefits, which
OL,14,Fgrew during the pandemic and has
OL,15,Fremained high since.
OL,17,FThe Government hopes the proposals can
OL,18,Fsave #5 billion a year by the end of
OL,19,Fthe decade.
