OL,3,C#5 billion welfare cuts needed to
OL,4,C'save' system, Kendall to say
OL,6,F"Unless we ensure public money is
OL,7,Ffocused on those with the greatest
OL,8,Fneed and is spent in ways that have
OL,9,Fthe best chance of improving people's
OL,10,Flives, the risk is the welfare state
OL,11,Fwon't be there for people who really
OL,12,Fneed it in the future," she is
OL,13,Fexpected to say in a speech to the
OL,14,FInstitute for Public Policy Research
OL,15,Fthink tank.
OL,17,FShe will say the Government is
OL,18,F"grasping the nettle of welfare
OL,19,Freform. Not for the sake of it, but to
OL,20,Fsave it".
