OL,3,C#5 billion welfare cuts needed to
OL,4,C'save' system, Kendall to say
OL,6,FThe aim is to give people
OL,7,F"opportunities" so they can "build a
OL,8,Fbetter life", she will say.
OL,10,FThe Government appears intent to press
OL,11,Fahead with the plans amid mounting
OL,12,Fopposition.
OL,14,FSome 100 Labour MPs ` more than a
OL,15,Fquarter of the party's parliamentary
OL,16,Fnumbers ` are reported to have signed
OL,17,Fa letter urging ministers to scale
OL,18,Fback welfare cuts under consideration.
